               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was coming over the Bridge from the Borough—two young men were walking before me—they turned off, one one was and one another—the gentleman turned round and laid hold of me—I did not know what it was for—he went four or five yards from me, said picked up his handkerchief—I went on till he met the policeman, and gave me in charge.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. DEAN</hi>.—It was not half a yard from him that I picked it up.</p>
